snippet.textDisplay:
For all those people saying, anything besides 'Punjabi folk' is all crap ...I just want to say 2 things:

1. Coke Studio is all about fusion, and that't the beauty of it.
2. Coke Studio people are much more informed than us on what they create - so let them play & let's enjoy it.

I loved it to the core, including the chorus & the Punjabi piece. 

#Peace

snippet.textDisplay: Everytime I listen to the song, I grow more fond of Des Raj Lachkani Jatha and more annoyed with the Hindi lyrics and music they produced for this song. This is not fusion! This is straight up screwing a perfect song in the name of fusion. But unfortunately no more sources are available for us to listen to this legendary Jatha.
